					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I real liked this SCP, some how the idea of exsepting a time loop seems vary original, as apposed to the torture other time loops seem to focuses on.</p> <p>Also think about this, if the Foundation releases him, their going to be doing a major A-class targeted amnestic routines. Which is to say, someone has to choices between forcing SCP-2265 to loses all his new knowledge, or live the rest of his life in captivity.</p> <p>Their goes that happy ending.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
